raw_body:
Avoid conflicts in reading the same register mmPCIE_INDEX2
with other clients

Change-Id: Iff93db1d47b732ef993ff1a37ad3778c44253da0
Signed-off-by: Rex Zhu <Rex.Zhu@amd.com>
---
