 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/gfx_v11_0.c  | 52 +-----------------------
 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/gfx_v12_0.c  | 52 +-----------------------
 4 files changed, 57 insertions(+), 102 deletions(-)

