>
> Change-Id: Iced6ed3698167296c97b14e7e4569883859d619c
> Signed-off-by: Yong Zhao <Yong.Zhao@amd.com>
> ---
>   drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu_amdkfd.c    |  9 +++--
